title: Living Favor-Minded

description:
God wants to show you an abundant increase of favor, but if you’re not releasing your faith, it will limit what He can do. That’s why Joel wants to teach you in this empowering message how to develop a favor mentality.----Visit https://joelosteen.com to receive daily updates and encouragement from Joel Osteen.----Have you followed Joel Osteen on Instagram? https://instagram.com/joelosteen.
